{"tid":928434,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"【BUG是定理】Windows 10 更新再爆BUG，今次連Office文件都儲存不了","createTime":"2018-12-04T23:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T18:40:19.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"629d718cfe9fa65b1a29425301ed6c9e95bdb04d","tid":928434,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:23:27.000Z","msg":"最近，微軟就承認了在 Windows 10 的十月更新（Version 1809）中存在另一個嚴重的問題，導致公司決定在更多的PC設備上進行阻止升級。<br />\n<br />\n這個問題發現於微軟和 Morphisec的共同調查，他們調查後發現 Morphisec 系統開發套件存在某些潛在問題，如果用戶發現了這些潛解決方式，會讓微軟 Office 無法正常工作。<br />\n<br />\n微軟在 Windows 10 Version 1809 的狀態頁面中寫道「微軟和 Morphisec 已經確認在安裝 Morphisec Protector 或者其他使用 Morphisec 軟件開發工具（SDK）開發的軟件（包括Cisco AMP for Endpoints）的設備上存在問題。這些應用可能導致用戶無法正常保存微軟Office文檔。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/12/04/windows-10-oct2018-update-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2Fwindows-10-oct2018-update-bug%2F&d=1sVcEiuYA9%2FCtHdq16%2FHB9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=53386df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/12/04/windows-10-oct2018-update-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"e69bce55990fce3bc40547bbc47610db73d6354d","tid":928434,"uid":9338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:41:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老味次次更新完都總會有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a3aaba25c2c05c9a725859ee46b52e9f204d8e","tid":928434,"uid":153941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"吊 唔怪得save完冇撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4e763840350ca3a653c76c8fe03d0d96e76fc3","tid":928434,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"so? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02649e38f74d39802f84c7545651a99aee7a1e4c","tid":928434,"uid":1499